thread.title: Fed Set to Raise Rates, Issue New Economic Projections

author: Nick Timiraos
title: Fed Set to Raise Rates, Issue New Economic Projections

organizations.name: issue new economic projections the federal reserve

text:
The Federal Reserve is likely to raise short-term interest rates by a quarter percentage point after its two-day policy meeting concludes Wednesday, the sixth such move since late 2015.

The biggest questions will be answered when officials release new projections for unemployment, inflation, economic growth and interest rates in the years...
